agents_and_skills.template:
Delegate to one of these subagents:
{agent_list}

Pass these skills to the subagent: {skill_list}

Append to your Task prompt: "Use the Skill tool to invoke [skill-name]. Report which skill(s) you used."

Skip delegation ONLY if this is a purely informational request with no implementation.

skills_only.template:
Use these skill(s) for this request: {skill_list}

Invoke with: Skill(skill="[skill-name]")

If delegating to a subagent, instruct them to invoke the skill and report back.
